### List open conversations
GET https://api.gettalko.com/v1/conversations?status=OPEN&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{TALKO_API_KEY}}

### Send a message to a conversation
POST https://api.gettalko.com/v1/conversations/{{CONVERSATION_ID}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{TALKO_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello from the customer integration kit.",
  "sender": "AGENT"
}

### Fetch visitor context for a conversation
GET https://api.gettalko.com/v1/conversations/{{CONVERSATION_ID}}/visitor-context
Authorization: Bearer {{TALKO_API_KEY}}
